WEBVTT

00:00.300 --> 00:02.134
<i>Previously on Mad Men...</i>

00:02.350 --> 00:04.609
He is not your friend,
he is the enemy.

00:05.495 --> 00:07.337
You let Don talk,
you should know better.

00:07.433 --> 00:08.849
The guy's not a salesman.

00:08.952 --> 00:11.332
- Why do we care what that guy wants?
- Because he's a client.

00:11.972 --> 00:13.365
I don't want to live on
the Upper East side.

00:13.463 --> 00:16.603
I saw us raising our kids in a place
with more different kinds of people.

00:18.306 --> 00:19.541
I don't know what to say.

00:19.649 --> 00:23.361
Say you're gonna be the first American
to complete a successful heart transplant.

00:23.770 --> 00:26.183
I could come up and
stay there tonight, if you want.

00:27.421 --> 00:28.764
We'll be fine.

00:31.069 --> 00:33.608
<i>( theme music playing )</i>

